<br>
What you wanna do is send in a couple FD'ers to FD along the route to the west wall and tell the raid when it's clear. Send in 2 groups invis to run to the WW camp and clear there. Once they've cleared the general area, send in the rest of the raid. Only really big thing to remember is to stand and die if you get aggro. Consent an FD puller to drag your corpse, but otherwise, stand and die. If you get hit by one of those translocating imps, stay put for 3-4 seconds to ensure that you don't get aggro before returning to the camp.<br>
<br>
Oh, and have a shaman/enchanter with you... those imps translocate you a lot shorter distance if they're crippled.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
-Aurianne<br>
