Cool, I never even realized that part Aurianne...  Always just seemed to be random to me, just like phase spiders in DN.<br>
<br>
Gremli, it could help a lot if you have a CoH mage with you also as part of the break in team.  A monk/sk with sow/soe can intercept and lead away mobs from both the portal, and wanderers that come within visual range of the west wall.  Once they lead the mobs far enough away, the mage calls them back clearing the aggro.  Then you can take the mobs as they trickle back in.  Makes for a much easier break.<br>
