<br>
I've camped portal a few times just for yucks. As an enchanter, super heavy crowd control is very fun and since there are a number of wanderers that see invis that path past the portal, you can just hang out by the portal until your jumped. Then get adds. Then get more adds. And still more adds.<br>
<br>
Okay. With 1 group with insanely great equipment we stayed alive until myself and the cleric ran out of mana.<br>
<br>
With 2 groups we stayed alive longer but with the same final result.<br>
<br>
Now, there are a number of techniques that could actually allow you to live and camp at the portal - which would be kinda interesting just to prove a point (i.e. it could be done) but getting out of traffic patterns and limiting the shadow step arc are clever things to do that you *should* take advantage of. Save yourself the headache of a portal corpse recovery, break in and hold the west wall.<br>
